                            <comment id="17239631" author="luciferyang" created="Fri, 27 Nov 2020 11:07:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems that changing value of &quot;spark.network.timeout&quot; doesn&apos;t really change the value of&#160;STORAGE_BLOCKMANAGER_HEARTBEAT_TIMEOUT and their relationship is maintained by code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, the treatment of &quot;spark.shuffle.io.connectionTimeout&quot; is as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/** Connect timeout in milliseconds. Default 120 secs. */&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; connectionTimeoutMs() {
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; defaultNetworkTimeoutS = JavaUtils.timeStringAsSec(
    conf.get(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;spark.network.timeout&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;120s&quot;&lt;/span&gt;));
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; defaultTimeoutMs = JavaUtils.timeStringAsSec(
    conf.get(SPARK_NETWORK_IO_CONNECTIONTIMEOUT_KEY, defaultNetworkTimeoutS + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;s&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)) * 1000;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;) defaultTimeoutMs;
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But it seems that there is no similar treatment forSTORAGE_BLOCKMANAGER_HEARTBEAT_TIMEOUT in HeartbeatReceiver and&#160;MesosCoarseGrainedSchedulerBackend&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; val executorTimeoutMs = sc.conf.get(config.STORAGE_BLOCKMANAGER_HEARTBEAT_TIMEOUT)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
mesosExternalShuffleClient.get
  .registerDriverWithShuffleService(
    agent.hostname,
    externalShufflePort,
    sc.conf.get(config.STORAGE_BLOCKMANAGER_HEARTBEAT_TIMEOUT),
    sc.conf.get(config.EXECUTOR_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL))
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maybe need to be fixed by code changes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
